WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:01.483
Olgu!

00:00:01.483 --> 00:00:04.383
Anname su rakendusele pﾃ､ris domeeni automaatse

00:00:04.383 --> 00:00:04.866
TLS-iga.

00:00:04.866 --> 00:00:07.766
Neli lﾃｼhikest sammu ja oled internetis.

00:00:08.534 --> 00:00:10.030
Siin on tee.

00:00:10.030 --> 00:00:12.024
Hangi Cloudflare API token,

00:00:12.024 --> 00:00:13.519
seadista infrastruktuur CLI-s,

00:00:13.519 --> 00:00:16.510
tﾃｵuka see serverisse ja juuruta Traefik

00:00:16.510 --> 00:00:17.009
proksi,

00:00:17.009 --> 00:00:19.1000
mis tegeleb DNS-i ja sertifikaatidega sinu

00:00:19.1000 --> 00:00:20.498
eest.

00:00:21.269 --> 00:00:24.040
Esmalt ava Cloudflare'i juhtpaneel oma brauseris.

00:00:24.040 --> 00:00:25.426
Mine My Profile,

00:00:25.426 --> 00:00:26.811
siis API Tokens,

00:00:26.811 --> 00:00:29.582
ja loo token Zone DNS Edit

00:00:29.582 --> 00:00:30.044
ﾃｵigusega,

00:00:30.044 --> 00:00:32.815
et CLI saaks su kirjeid hallata.

00:00:36.109 --> 00:00:37.105
Teine samm.

00:00:37.105 --> 00:00:39.098
ﾃ徼leme CLI-le avaliku IP,

00:00:39.098 --> 00:00:39.596
baasdomﾃ､ni,

00:00:39.596 --> 00:00:42.585
sertifikaadi e-posti ja Cloudflare API tokeni.

00:00:42.585 --> 00:00:45.573
Sertifikaadi e-post ja token on jagatud

00:00:45.573 --> 00:00:47.566
kﾃｵigi sinu masinate vahel,

00:00:47.566 --> 00:00:50.555
seega seadistad need ainult ﾃｼks kord.

00:00:51.355 --> 00:00:53.706
Infrastruktuur salvestatud sinu konfiguratsiooni.

00:00:57.020 --> 00:00:57.513
Kinnitame,

00:00:57.513 --> 00:00:59.978
et infrastruktuuri seaded on salvestatud.

00:00:59.978 --> 00:01:00.964
Avalik IP,

00:01:00.964 --> 00:01:01.458
baasdomeen,

00:01:01.458 --> 00:01:04.416
sertifikaadi e-post -- kﾃｵik on konfiguratsioonis

00:01:04.416 --> 00:01:04.909
nﾃ､htav.

00:01:06.659 --> 00:01:07.631
Seaded salvestatud.

00:01:07.631 --> 00:01:09.088
Valmis serverisse tﾃｵugatamiseks.

00:01:12.441 --> 00:01:13.636
Kolmas samm.

00:01:13.636 --> 00:01:15.429
Tﾃｵukame konfiguratsiooni serverisse.

00:01:15.429 --> 00:01:18.417
See loob DNS-kirjed Cloudflare'is automaatselt

00:01:18.417 --> 00:01:21.404
ja valmistab proksi konfiguratsiooni masinas

00:01:21.404 --> 00:01:22.002
ette.

00:01:25.002 --> 00:01:25.910
Tﾃｵugatud.

00:01:25.910 --> 00:01:28.633
DNS-kirjeid luuakse Cloudflare'is.

00:01:31.986 --> 00:01:33.612
Algab neljas samm.

00:01:33.612 --> 00:01:36.322
Loome vﾃ､ikese repositooriumi nimega infra.

00:01:36.322 --> 00:01:39.033
Siin hakkab proksi elama --

00:01:39.033 --> 00:01:40.659
isoleeritud rakenduse repositooriumidest.

00:01:43.659 --> 00:01:45.148
Infra repo loodud.

00:01:45.148 --> 00:01:47.133
Isoleeritud su rakenduse repodest.

00:01:50.468 --> 00:01:52.421
Rakendame sisseehitatud proksi malli.

00:01:52.421 --> 00:01:55.350
See sisaldab Traefikut koos Let's Encrypt

00:01:55.350 --> 00:01:57.790
ja Cloudflare DNS-01 vﾃ､ljakutsete konfiguratsiooniga,

00:01:57.790 --> 00:01:58.279
tﾃｶﾃｶvalmis.

00:02:00.529 --> 00:02:02.331
Traefiku konfiguratsioon paigas.

00:02:05.605 --> 00:02:07.050
Ja kﾃ､ivitame proksi.

00:02:07.050 --> 00:02:09.940
Traefik avastab sinu konteinerid iga viie

00:02:09.940 --> 00:02:10.904
sekundi jﾃ､rel.

00:02:10.904 --> 00:02:13.794
TLS sertifikaadid tulevad Let's Encryptist automaatselt.

00:02:13.794 --> 00:02:16.684
Sinu rakendus on nﾃｼﾃｼd internetis HTTPS

00:02:16.684 --> 00:02:17.647
kaudu kﾃ､ttesaadav.

00:02:17.647 --> 00:02:19.383
Proksi on tﾃｶﾃｶs.

00:02:19.383 --> 00:02:21.696
TLS sertifikaadid saabuvad automaatselt.

00:02:22.445 --> 00:02:25.207
Ja sellega on vﾃｵrgustamine korras!

00:02:25.207 --> 00:02:26.311
Kohtumiseni jﾃ､rgmises.
